'''R6''' is an [[Highways in Slovakia|expressway]] in [[Slovakia]]. It currently connects the [[Motorway D1 (Slovakia)|D1]] with [[Púchov]] as a feeder at the length of 6.6&nbsp;km and is signed as a national road 49A. There are plans to extend it to the border of the [[Czech Republic]].
The total planned length is 23&nbsp;km and construction will begin around year 2010.

